---
---

<section class="py-20 md:py-28">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-charcoal">
        Field services haven't changed in 30 years
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        Energy and water companies manage dozens of agency relationships independently.
        Procurement is slow, data is siloed, and there's no cross-industry visibility.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-red-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Fragmented relationships</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Each agency has its own contract, data format, and performance tracking. Internal FTE is spent managing suppliers rather than driving outcomes.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-amber-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">No cross-industry visibility</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Performance data is trapped in silos. There are no industry benchmarks, no best practice sharing, and no way to compare agencies objectively.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-orange-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Increased data risk</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Multiple data interfaces with multiple agencies multiply data breach risk. Each connection is another attack surface in a heavily regulated environment.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
